Name:                haskell-simple-todo
Version:             0.1.0
Homepage:            https://github.com/xddq/haskell-simple-todo
Bug-reports:         https://github.com/xddq/haskell-simple-todo
Author:              Pierre Dahmani <hi@pierre-dev.com>
